# The Family Crisis

## Key Issues
- 40% of children are born to unmarried mothers.
- 70% of Black children grow up without fathers.
-  Family breakdown leads to poverty, crime, and mental health issues.

## Proposed Solutions
1. Remove marriage penalties in welfare programs.
2. Introduce tax incentives for married families.
3. Regulate Big Tech to prevent harm to children.

